# Happy Bites

A collaborative food website project developed by our team.

## Features
- Food browsing
- User-friendly UI
- Responsive design

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Flask/Django (tell me which one)
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Bootstrap

## My Contribution
- UI development
- Frontend sections
- Collaboration and debugging

## Team Project
Built with friends using Antigravity.

